  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* Fix a potential panic by @TomWright in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/393\r\n* Bump golang.org/x/net from 0.21.0 to 0.22.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/396\r\n* Bump github.com/alecthomas/chroma/v2 from 2.12.0 to 2.13.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/399\r\n* Bump github.com/pelletier/go-toml/v2 from 2.1.1 to 2.2.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/401\r\n* Bump github.com/pelletier/go-toml/v2 from 2.2.0 to 2.2.1 by @dependabot in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/403\r\n* Bump golang.org/x/net from 0.22.0 to 0.24.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/402\r\n* Don't include timestamp in generated manpages by @guilherme-puida in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/405\r\n* Bump github.com/pelletier/go-toml/v2 from 2.2.1 to 2.2.2 by @dependabot in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/407\r\n* Bump golang.org/x/text from 0.14.0 to 0.15.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/408\r\n* Bump golang.org/x/net from 0.24.0 to 0.25.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/409\r\n* add support for resolving YAML aliases by @pmeier in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/415\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @pmeier made their first contribution in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/415\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/compare/v2.7.0...v2.8.0",
